com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.plan

Class PlanRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.plan.PlanRecord

  • public class PlanRecord
extends Object
    List record representing a Plan, from the list returned in the PlanListResponse. A Plan describes the available application features granted to an Account, as well as the details and units used for billing this Account.
    Author:
    Chris Wright
